data.description: This custom built, full brick, single story home is only 6 years young and features 4 bedrooms, an office and 3.5 baths. Beautiful wood floors throughout main living area, freshly painted, granite countertops, secluded master suite, large Great Room with fireplace, split floor plan, wainscotting, large back yard and so much more! The large kitchen features an Island, gas stove, lots of cupboard and counter space, pantry, crown molding and recessed lighting. Master bath features glass shower, soaking tub, double vanity and walk in closet. Conveniently located to all Madison and Huntsville has to offer. Home is priced to sell and can close fast.
